" data-element-type=\"paragraph\" data-version=\"5\" id=\"1877144597\" style=\"text-align: left;\"> <h4><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: unset;\">tire service</span></h4> \n</div> \n <div class=\"u_1739120614 dmNewParagraph\" data-element-type=\"paragraph\" data-version=\"5\" id=\"1739120614\" style=\"transition: none 0s ease 0s; text-align: left; display: block;\"><p><span style=\"display: unset; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Enhance safety and fuel efficiency with tire rotations, alignments, and replacements for optimal traction.</span></p></div> \n <a data-display-type=\"block\" class=\"u_1107706337 align-center dmButtonLink dmWidget dmWwr default dmOnlyButton dmDefaultGradient\" file=\"false\" href=\"services/tires.html\" data-element-type=\"dButtonLinkId\" id=\"1107706337\" link_type=\"LINK_DYNAMIC_PAGE\"> <span class=\"iconBg\" aria-hidden=\"true\" id=\"1855297428\"> <span class=\"icon hasFontIcon icon-star\" id=\"1430511449\"></span> \n</span> \n <span class=\"text\" id=\"1492375231\">Visit Page &gt;</span> \n</a> \n</div> \n</div> \n</div> \n</div> \n</div> \n</div> \n <div class=\"u_1218616934 dmRespRow\" id=\"1218616934\"> <div class=\"dmRespColsWrapper\" id=\"1348507957\"> <div class=\"u_1510536674 dmRespCol small-12 large-undefined medium-undefined large-0 medium-0 dmSectionNoParallax medium-6 large-6\" id=\"1510536674\" data-gallery-bg=\"eyJzbGlkZXMiOlsiaHR0cHM6Ly9pcnAuY2RuLXdlYnNpdGUuY29tLzE2MmZmNGUzL2RtczNyZXAvbXVsdGkvc2VjdGlvbi1iZzExLWFic3RyYWN0LXNoYXBlcy01NGMwYjRjMC5zdmciXX0=\" data-anim-desktop=\"none\"> <div class=\"u_1642452296 imageWidget align-center hide-for-small\" data-element-type=\"image\" data-widget-type=\"image\" id=\"1642452296\"><img src=\"https://lirp.cdn-website.com/162ff4e3/dms3rep/multi/opt/Central+-+Header-1920w.jpg\" alt=\"Central Garage Front | Green Drop Garage\" id=\"1748241734\" class=\"\" data-dm-image-path=\"../irp.cdn-website.com/162ff4e3/dms3rep/multi/Central+-+Header.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1920\" onerror=\"handleImageLoadError(this)\"></div> \n <div class=\"u_1813740440 imageWidget align-center\" data-element-type=\"image\" data-widget-type=\"image\" id=\"1813740440\"><img src=\"https://lirp.cdn-website.com/162ff4e3/dms3rep/multi/opt/Garage+1-1920w.JPG\" alt=\"Shop Garage | Green Drop Garage\" id=\"1438839174\" class=\"\" data-dm-image-path=\"../irp.cdn-website.com/162ff4e3/dms3rep/multi/Garage+1.JPG\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1440\" onerror=\"handleImageLoadError(this)\"></div> \n</div> \n <div class=\"u_1504738854 dmRespCol small-12 medium-6 large-6\" id=\"1504738854\"> <div class=\"u_1899176316 dmRespRow\" id=\"1899176316\"> <div class=\"dmRespColsWrapper\" id=\"1295580048\"> <div class=\"dmRespCol large-12 medium-12 small-12 u_1515179166\" id=\"1515179166\"> <div class=\"u_1021191145 dmNewParagraph\" data-element-type=\"paragraph\" data-version=\"5\" id=\"1021191145\" data-styletopreserve=\"{\" background-image\":\"\"}\"=\"\" data-diy-text=\"\" new-inline-bind-applied=\"true\"> <h2><span class=\"\" style=\"display: unset; color: var(--color_2);\"><span style=\"display: unset; color: var(--color_2);\">Welcome to</span> \n</span> \n<span style=\"display: initial; color: var(--color_2);\"><span class=\"inline-data-binding\" data-encoded-value=\"R3JlZW4gRHJvcCBHYXJhZ2U=\" data-inline-binding=\"content_library.global.company_name\">Green Drop Garage</span></span></h2> \n</div> \n <div class=\"u_1287693308 dmDividerWrapper clearfix\" data-element-type=\"dDividerId\" data-layout=\"divider-style-1\" data-widget-version=\"2\" id=\"1287693308\" layout=\"divider-gradient-line\"><hr class=\"dmDivider\" style=\"border-width:2px; border-top-style:solid; color:grey;\" id=\"1678653952\"></div> \n</div> \n</div> \n</div> \n <div class=\"dmRespRow u_1591025013\" id=\"1591025013\"> <div class=\"dmRespColsWrapper\" id=\"1217911757\"> <div class=\"dmRespCol large-12 medium-12 small-12\" id=\"1972506729\"> <div class=\"dmNewParagraph\" data-element-type=\"paragraph\" data-version=\"5\" id=\"1788710682\"> <h3 style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\"><span style=\"display: unset;\">Eco-Friendly, Full-Service Auto Care</span></h3> \n</div> \n <div class=\"dmNewParagraph\" data-element-type=\"paragraph\" data-version=\"5\" id=\"1819933054\"><p><span style=\"display: unset;\">Welcome to Green Drop Garage, your go-to eco-conscious, full-service auto repair shop in the Portland, OR, and Vancouver, WA areas. With six locations across Portland and Vancouver, Green Drop Garage is committed to keeping your vehicle in top shape while protecting the environment. Our ASE-certified technicians handle all makes and models with precision and care, and as a proud NAPA AutoCare Center, we back our work with a 24-month/24k-mile nationwide warranty on parts and labor. When you step into Green Drop Garage, expect a warm welcome with a Stumptown cold brew in hand, an attentive ear to your car concerns, and absolutely no pushy upsells—just genuine service.</span></p></div> \n</div> \n</div> \n</div> \n <div class=\"dmRespRow u_1151733083\" id=\"1151733083\"> <div class=\"dmRespColsWrapper\" id=\"1735831069\"> <div class=\"dmRespCol large-12 medium-12 small-12\" id=\"1727053033\"> <div class=\"dmNewParagraph\" data-element-type=\"paragraph\" data-version=\"5\" id=\"1470505763\" data-diy-text=\"\"> <h3 style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\"><span style=\"display: unset;\">Sustainable Practices, Community Focused</span></h3> \n</div> \n <div class=\"dmNewParagraph\" data-element-type=\"paragraph\" data-version=\"5\" id=\"1403519684\"><p><span class=\"\" style=\"display: unset;\"><span style=\"display: unset;\">Green Drop Garage was founded on eco-friendly principles, beginning with converting diesel engines to run on vegetable oil and evolving into a full-scale green auto care facility. From recycling buildings for our shops to using re-refined oils and low-impact chemicals, every aspect of our service is designed to reduce our environmental footprint. We even provide eco-friendly</span> \n</span><a href=\"loaner-car.html\" runtime_url=\"/loaner-car\" type=\"page\" style=\"display: unset; color: var(--color_2); font-weight: bold;\">loaner cars</a><span class=\"\" style=\"display: unset;\"> <span style=\"display: unset;\">and a convenient</span> \n</span><a href=\"https://www.greendropgarage.com/memberships-old\" runtime_url=\"/memberships\" type=\"page\" style=\"display: unset; font-weight: bold; color: var(--color_2);\">concierge service</a><span style=\"display: unset;\">, ensuring a seamless and green experience for you. By choosing Green Drop Garage, you’re not only ensuring the safety and reliability of your vehicle, but also supporting a sustainable approach to car care that benefits our community and the planet.</span></p></div> \n</div> \n</div> \n</div> \n <div class=\"dmRespRow u_1660986496\" id=\"1660986496\"> <div class=\"dmRespColsWrapper\" id=\"1080800505\"> <div class=\"dmRespCol large-12 medium-12 small-12\" id=\"1842769900\"> <a data-display-type=\"block\" class=\"u_1716448960 align-center shopgenie-book-appt-btn dmButtonLink dmWidget dmWwr default dmOnlyButton dmDefaultGradient\" file=\"false\" data-element-type=\"dButtonLinkId\" id=\"1716448960\" title=\"Make an Appointment Online\" lock-element-for-editing=\"true\"> <span class=\"iconBg\" aria-hidden=\"true\" id=\"1819916975\"> <span class=\"icon hasFontIcon icon-star\" id=\"1609062448\"></span> \n</span> \n <span class=\"text\" id=\"1935627071\">Book Your Service</span> \n</a> \n <div class=\"u_1717355201 imageWidget align-center\" data-element-type=\"image\" data-widget-type=\"image\" id=\"1717355201\"><img src=\"https://lirp.cdn-website.com/162ff4e3/dms3rep/multi/Certified_B_Corporation_B_Corp_Logo_2022_Black_RGB.svg\" alt=\"\" id=\"1484391919\" class=\"\" width=\"103\" height=\"150\" data-dm-image-path=\"../irp.cdn-website.com/162ff4e3/dms3rep/multi/Certified_B_Corporation_B_Corp_Logo_2022_Black_RGB.svg\" onerror=\"handleImageLoadError(this)\"></div> \n</div> \n<